[thinking] **Exploring Graal Testing**
[thinking] 
[thinking] I'm considering how the Graal test plugin handles things. I think the Native image might run into issues if it calls getMethod on a test subclass without metadata. So, I wonder how to avoid reflecting on the test subclass. Should I use a real library class that overrides the old method signatures instead? It seems like the BasicComponentConfigurator might have the new signature, but I'm unsure about the old one.
[thinking] 
